name: Loren Roesler
description: Hi,my name is Loren,I put God first in everything I do. Am smart and very beautiful as I’ve been told many times. I enjoy the adventurous side of life specially when with someone I truly love. I like swimming,bowling,camping,reading,good movies,doesn’t misses sunrise or sunset whiles walking with my two dogs,Westie Terrier and a mongrel. Non of these is fun when doing it all alone.
